  "body": "### Description\r\nThe gas limit in the [Ethereum yellow paper](https://ethereum.github.io/yellowpaper/paper.pdf) is defined as a natural number, see page 7 (41). While its upper limit is not specified the [Ethereum reference tests](https://github.com/ethereum/tests/tree/develop/src/TransactionTestsFiller/ttGasLimit) specify it as 64-bit value. In the current implementation we use `long` for the nonce. The maximum positive value of `long` is `2^63 âˆ’ 1` which means it is less than the specified `2^64`.",
